## Development

#### Docs

Rebuild documentation pages from templates

    $ rake doc
    # Writing to mkdocs-material/docs/versions-main.md .. Done
    # ...

Start documentation app

    $ cd mkdocs
    $ mkdocs serve

Open http://localhost:8000/

